    "If it takes more than 10 minutes, it's not Chill. Record, transcript, tidy, done. Keep it light, keep it fast." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Wenn es länger als 10 Minuten dauert, ist es nicht mehr chillig. Aufnehmen, transkribieren, ordnen, fertig. Bleib leicht, bleib schnell."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "If it takes more than 10 minutes, it's not Chill. Record, transcript, tidy, done. Keep it light, keep it fast."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Si tarda más de 10 minutos, no es Chill. Grabar, transcribir, ordenar, listo. Mantenlo ligero, mantenlo rápido."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Si cela prend plus de 10 minutes, ce n'est pas Chill. Enregistrez, transcrivez, rangez, c'est fait. Gardez-le léger, restez rapide."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "10分以上かかる場合はチルではありません。記録、書き起こし、整理整頓、完了。軽く、速く保ちます。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "10분 이상 걸리면 Chill이 아닙니다. 녹음, 녹취록, 정리, 완료. 가볍게 유지하고 빠르게 유지하세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "如果超过10分钟，就不是Chill。记录，抄本，整洁，完成。保持轻，保持快。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "如果超過10分鐘，就不是Chill。記錄，抄本，整潔，完成。保持輕，保持快。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "In a digital era of \"silent communication,\" we often suppress emotion." : {
